org.jboss.windup.rules.apps.java.model

Interface JavaClassFileModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FileModel, ResourceModel, com.tinkerpop.frames.VertexFrame, WindupVertexFrame

    public interface JavaClassFileModel
extends FileModel
    This Model represents Java class files on disk (eg, /path/to/Foo.class). This does not represent Java source files (.java files). The class itself is represented by the JavaClassModel frame.
